{{SupportPage|vendor=Belkin|vs_id_old=5482}} This device is identical to the [[Belkin F7D2301]]. The default SSID is '''Belkin.XXXX''' where '''XXXX''' appears to '''3''' followed by the last three hex digits of the wireless interface MAC address (though this could be incorrect). An example SSID is '''Belkin.3147''' with MAC 94:44:52:8D:C1:47. "P/N: 141700520021J R0B" appears to be silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
